/a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/ps4">PS4</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/ps5">PS5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-one">Xbox One</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-series-x">Xbox Series X</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox-series-s">Xbox Series S</a>版本。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511769" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511769" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3511769" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-of-duty-zombies-trailer-call-of-duty-next-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511769" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视</figcaption></figure><p>有两个版本可供预订 - 标准版和 Vault 版。前者包含游戏、早期开放测试版和战役、灵魂收割机示踪武器蓝图和僵尸幽灵干员皮肤。</p><p>另一方面，Vault 版本包括上述所有内容以及两个武器库、包含超过 7,000 个<em>使命召唤</em>点数物品的 BlackCell Battle Pass 捆绑包、30 个等级跳跃以及 Nemesis Operator Pack。</p><p>现在预购 Vault 版本的人还可以使用 Soap Operator Pack，该包可在<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/games/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-2"><em>《现代战争 2》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/games/call-of-duty-warzone"><em>《战区》</em></a>中立即解锁。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-may-be-